        .card-reveal.pink.darken-3
          %blockquote
            %span.card-title.white-text Ufuoma 'UU' Umusu
          %i.material-icons.right close
          %p.white-text Ufuoma 'UU' Umusu is a graduate of English and Literary Studies from the University of Port Harcourt. She has professional certifications from Lagos Business School, Pan Atlantic School of Media and Communications in Media Enterprise, and Screenwriting for TV, Film and New Media.
          %p.white-text She is an Actress, Television Presenter, Model, Image Consultant, Events promoter, and Venue Stylist. She has been a red carpet host at the City People Fashion and Style Awards.
          %p.white-text Her Image consulting and event management practice includes working for various Nigerian and foreign based companies in the fashion, design, beauty and lifestyle sectors. She has carved a niche for working with Nigerians in the diaspora who have headed back home to create sustainable businesses to fill up the Nigerian employment gap.
          %p.white-text Her company (Ufuoma Umusu Nigeria Ltd) manages communication strategies in the areas of branding, editorial, social media and press releases. She is the 'Editor-In-Chic' of www.uunista.com and currently a post graduate student majoring in Media and Communication studies.
          %p.white-text In 2013 She was a guest on the Femina Speaks Radio show with Ese Walter when the show debuted at the Love FM Studios, Abuja. She is currently one of the hosts at Femina Speaks TV.
          %p.white-text Connect with Ufuoma 'UU' Umusu :
          %p.white-text www.uunista.com, uunista@gmail.com, events@abujaweddingplanner.com(event coordination and planning).
